 href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/message_event\"><code>message</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/open_event\"><code>open</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Die Eigenschaft <code><strong>WebSocket.onclose</strong></code> ist ein <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code>, der aufgerufen wird, wenn die Eigenschaft <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/readyState\" title=\"WebSocket.readyState\"><code>WebSocket.readyState</code></a> zu <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/readyState\" title=\"CLOSED\"><code>CLOSED</code></a> geändert bzw. die Verbindung geschlossen wird.</p>\n\n<p>Als Parameter übergeben wird ein <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CloseEvent\"><code>CloseEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>aWebSocket</em>.onclose = function(event) {\n  console.log(\"WebSocket is closed now.\");\n};</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"wert","title":"Wert","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>EventListener</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   